TEXT 472 88 Left 2 ;Sizing:\n \n1) Set reference current -> 1 mA\n2) Iref = (Vcc-Vbe)/R1 -> R1 = (Vcc-Vbe)/R1 = (12-0.6)/1m =11.4k\n \nOutput resistance Rout = ?
TEXT 464 584 Left 2 ;The following relation holds: Io/Iref = R3/R4\n \nSizing:\n1) Set Iref = I(R2) = 1mA\n2) Set V(R3) = 1 V -> R3 = 1k ohm\n3) If we want Io = 2 Iref -> R3/R4 = 2 -> R4 = 500 ohm\n4) R is given by R = (Vcc - Vbe - V(R3))/Iref = (12-0.6-1)/1m = 10.4 k ohm
